title: #92Noon Live From TCO: Florio/Amundson/Colquit
description: PA & Nordo deep dive both sides of the ball for the upcoming Vikings showdown in San Francisco.  Mike Florio calls in to join the Vikings deep diving.  Cy Amundson, local comedian and Vikings.com contributor, stops by the TCO studios to have some fun at the Saints expense.  Vikings punter, Britton Colquitt, also joins in-studio to talk about his past history with Levi's Stadium in San Francisco where the Vikings will take on the 9ers.
